snippet.title: Curly Monkey (Chinese plug & play console game)
snippet.description:
well you've seen Curly Monkey 2 already, now see where everyones favourite monkey came from. Its okay! but harder than the 2nd because you can only take one hit.

System: VT03 / Developed by Nice Code / Recorded from DreamGear Motion Control 130 in 1 (NTSC)
